Requirements: python-twisted

$ python snurr.py -h
usage: snurr.py [-h] [-s] SERVER PORT CHANNEL LISTEN_PORT

Pipes UDP-messages to an IRC-channel.

positional arguments:
  SERVER       IRC server
  PORT         IRC server port
  CHANNEL      IRC channel (without the '#')
  LISTEN_PORT  UDP listener port

optional arguments:
  -h, --help   show this help message and exit
  -s, --ssl    connect with SSL
